description: Austin is feeling pretty awestruck by the insanely tasty selection of sweet & savory creations from Crepe Crazy.After gaining many foodie fans at their two brick & mortar locations, you can now find this cool truck at many fantastic events and fests around town, battering up their famous flat French treats. Their delectable selection includes favorites like Ham & Swiss, Florentine, and Caprese, all filled with freshness and folded to perfection. On the sweet side, you’ve got Lemon Zest Dust, Nutella Royale, or Brown Sugar & Cinnamon. And there’s so much more to enjoy on their mouthwatering menu. Head your way to Crepe Crazy (or invite them to come cater your next exciting party) for crepes that you’ll crave to a kooky degree.
name: Crepe Crazy
